Splunk-alert_microsoftteams

Splunk App to send notifications to Microsoft Teams Custom alert action to send messages to Microsoft Teams. This is a fork from alert_msteams that was written by Abhi Devireddy who appears to have abandonded it. It has been reworked in Python3 and using requests.

PRs Welcome

Only setup is going to an alert search and adding the Webhook URL and if there is an action field add it so it will parse correctly.

https://github.com/MattLParker/Splunk-alert_microsoftteams